=== 外国驻蓉领事机构 ===
{{主条目|成都领事机构列表}}

目前成都实际有外国领事机构共16个，5个已达成协议待开馆，另有2个已（暂）闭馆。此外，[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]计划在成都设立领事馆。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Abertura de novas repartições consulares do Brasil no exterior|url=https://www.gov.br/mre/pt-br/canais_atendimento/imprensa/notas-a-imprensa/abertura-de-novas-reparticoes-consulares-do-brasil-no-exterior|access-date=2022-01-31|work=Ministério das Relações Exteriores|language=pt-br|archive-date=2022-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220304020141/https://www.gov.br/mre/pt-br/canais_atendimento/imprensa/notas-a-imprensa/abertura-de-novas-reparticoes-consulares-do-brasil-no-exterior|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Argentina expects to jump aboard the BRI express|url=https://en.ndrc.gov.cn/news/mediarusources/202112/t20211203_1306888.html|access-date=2022-01-31|author=China Daily|work=National Development and Reform Commission (NDRC) People's Republic of China|language=en|archive-date=2022-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220304045128/https://en.ndrc.gov.cn/news/mediarusources/202112/t20211203_1306888.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

